OL,3,CThree arrests made amid Al Quds Day
OL,4,Cdemonstration and counter-protest
OL,6,FThree arrests have been made amid a
OL,7,Fprotest and counter-protest for Al
OL,8,FQuds Day, police said.
OL,10,FAl Quds Day demonstrators chanted
OL,11,F"from the river to the sea" and held
OL,12,Fpictures of the late leader of Iran at
OL,13,Fa static protest in London on Sunday.
OL,15,FScotland Yard had braced for a
OL,16,F"difficult public order" environment,
OL,17,Fwith at least 1,000 officers drafted
OL,18,Fin to manage the crowd.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@[O]xD@AOUxD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
