OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1773659109
OL,3,CThree arrests made amid Al Quds Day
OL,4,Cdemonstration and counter-protest
OL,6,FIn a post on X, the Metropolitan
OL,7,FPolice said: "Officers have made three
OL,8,Farrests, one for showing support for a
OL,9,Fproscribed organisation, one for
OL,10,Fdangerous driving and a third for
OL,11,Fthreatening and abusive behaviour."
OL,13,FHome Secretary Shabana Mahmood granted
OL,14,Fthe police's bid for a month-long ban
OL,15,Fon the annual march organised by the
OL,16,FIslamic Human Rights Commission
OL,17,F(IHRC), making it the first time such
OL,18,Fa restriction on protest had been
OL,19,Fimposed since 2012.
OL,26,@oD@NOUsD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
