OL,3,CThree arrests made amid Al Quds Day
OL,4,Cdemonstration and counter-protest
OL,6,FHowever, people could still legally
OL,7,Fassemble and take part in a so-called
OL,8,F"static protest".
OL,10,FHundreds of people began arriving from
OL,11,F1pm, many holding Palestine flags and
OL,12,Fbanners, some reading "Free Palestine"
OL,13,Fand "No to Israeli occupation".
OL,15,FThe annual Al Quds Day demonstration
OL,16,Fin London had drawn criticism over
OL,17,Fapparent backing for the Iranian
OL,18,Fregime after its organisers expressed
OL,19,Fsupport for the country's late leader.
