OL,3,CThree arrests made amid Al Quds Day
OL,4,Cdemonstration and counter-protest
OL,6,FA crowd of counter-protesters were
OL,7,Fseen on the opposite side of the
OL,8,FThames during a demonstration
OL,9,Forganised by Stop The Hate.
OL,11,FThey waved Israeli flags while one
OL,12,Fsign read "Hamas is terrorist".
OL,14,FPolice vans were parked along the road
OL,15,Fand on nearby Lambeth Bridge, while
OL,16,Ftwo police boats were seen on the
OL,17,FRiver Thames.
OL,26,@tD@KOUtD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
