PN,30705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1773659109
OL,3,CThree arrests made amid Al Quds Day
OL,4,Cdemonstration and counter-protest
OL,6,FIt is thought to be the first time
OL,7,Fthat Scotland Yard has used the river
OL,8,Fas a physical barrier to keep a large-
OL,9,Fscale protest and counter-protest
OL,10,Fapart.
OL,12,FAll protests and counter-protests had
OL,13,Fto take place between Vauxhall and
OL,14,FLambeth bridges, and were permitted
OL,15,Fbetween 1pm and 3pm, the Metropolitan
OL,16,FPolice said.
OL,18,FAl Quds Day is named after the Arabic
OL,19,Fname for Jerusalem and is usually held
OL,20,Fon the last Friday of Ramadan.
